<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Grooming Program Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #4caf50;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h2>Hello <%= userName %>,</h2>
    <p>Thank you for enrolling in our <strong>
            <%= programName %> Program
        </strong>. We have successfully received your application.
        Below are your enrollment details:</p>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Full Name:</strong></td>
            <td>
                <%= userName %>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Email:</strong></td>
            <td>
                <%= userEmail %>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Address:</strong></td>
            <td>
                <%= address %>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Program ID:</strong></td>
            <td>
                <%= programId %>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <p>We will contact you shortly with more details.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>Happy Paws BD</p>

    <hr />
    <p class="footer">This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
</body>

</html>